facilities {
  name: "Bob MacQuarrie Recreation Complex - Orléans"
  description:
    "This multipurpose facility provides users with a wide selection of services and amenities including a six-lane "
    "pool, diving boards and therapeutic pool. The complex also houses the Elizabeth Manley Figure Skating Arena, the "
    "Roger Sénécal Arena, squash and racquetball courts and a fitness centre. A variety of recreation programs are "
    "offered including fitness, fitness classes, summer camps, indoor cycling, aqua fitness, swimming lessons and "
    "general interest programs."
  source {
    url: "https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/place-listing/bob-macquarrie-recreation-complex-orleans"
