facilities {
  name: "Canterbury Recreation Complex"
  description:
    "The Canterbury Recreation Complex is the ideal place to meet your recreational needs. The facility boasts a 25 "
    "metre five lane swimming pool with sauna, an NHL sized ice rink in the Brian Kilrea Arena and the Canterbury "
    "Community Centre. Our pool offers a wide selection of aquatic programs including public swims, aquafitness and "
    "swimming lessons. Canterbury Recreation Complex offers a variety of programs for all ages. Through a partnership "
    "with the Canterbury Community Association, children's and adult programs are also available to the Canterbury "
    "community. These programs include: an after school program, adult and senior fitness programs, as well as art, "
    "dance, martial arts and yoga programs for all ages."
