facilities {
  name: "Champagne Fitness Centre"
  description:
    "The Champagne Fitness Centre is situated in a historic downtown building just a stone’s throw away from the "
    "ByWard Market. The facility houses a 22.86 metre (25 yards) four lane pool, weight and cardio rooms, sauna, and a "
    "mezzanine above the pool where the boxing programs are held. A large tile mural, Bathing in Champagne, is "
    "featured in the pool area."
