facilities {
  name: "Chapman Mills Community Building"
  description:
    "The Chapman Mills Community Building is in the heart of this Barrhaven neighbourhood. The building features a "
    "bright half-moon shaped main hall, a small kitchenette and 14 parking spaces, making it a popular spot for "
    "private rentals. City recreation programs and camps are offered at this location. Water Dragon Park, which "
    "features a children's play structure, splash pad and gazebo, is adjacent to the building."
  source {
    url: "https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/place-listing/chapman-mills-community-building"
