facilities {
  name: "Churchill Seniors Centre"
  description:
    "The centre offers a wide range of recreation programs for adults aged 50 and over. Programs include a variety of "
    "fitness classes you can register for, from Strength and Balance to yoga and even line dancing. Drop-in programs "
    "are available for those looking to play bridge or wanting to sing and play a ukulele. The facility has a "
    "programmed fitness centre, billiards equipment and a lounge."
