facilities {
  name: "Deborah Anne Kirwan Pool"
  description:
    "Deborah Anne Kirwan Pool is your tropical oasis in south Ottawa. With a leisure concept 25 metre main pool, "
    "wading pool with slide, whirl pool and sauna, there is something for everyone. Group swimming lessons for all "
    "ages, private lessons, March Break and summer camps are offered along with public swims. A variety of recreation "
    "programs are offered including swimming lessons for children, youth, adults and seniors."
