    "<li><span><strong>The facility is closed until further notice. </strong></span></li>\n"
    "<li><span><strong>The cardio and weight room is closed.</strong></span></li>\n"
    "</ul>\n"
    "<p><span>Heron Seniors Centre programs and drop-in activities are being offered at <a href=\"https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/recreation-facilities/facility-listing/carleton-heights-community-centre\">Carleton Heights Community Centre</a> (1665 Apeldoorn Avenue) during the closure.</span></p>\n"
    "<p><span>We are diligently working to bring our programs and services back to the Heron Road Community Centre. Thank you for your patience as we progress through this transition.</span></p>\n"
}
facilities {
  name: "Hintonburg Community Centre"
  description:
    "The Hintonburg Community Centre features a full size gym, a dance studio, and eight multi-purpose and meeting "
    "rooms that are ideal for events or meetings up to 125 people. The centre offers a wide range of recreational "
    "activities and programs for people of all ages. The centre is also accessible and offers a number of specialized "
    "programs for people with disabilities."
