facilities {
  name: "Jack Purcell Community Centre"
  description:
    "Centrally located in downtown Ottawa, Jack Purcell Community Centre has an 18 metre warm water pool, which offers "
    "regular aquatic programming and specialized programs for individuals with disabilities. The facility also has a "
    "fully accessible weight room, five meeting rooms of various sizes and access to an adjacent school gym. Jack "
    "Purcell offers a variety of programs for seniors, individuals with disabilities, and swimmers. Through a "
    "partnership with the Jack Purcell Recreation Association, children's and adult programs are also available to the "
    "Centretown community. These programs include: an after school program, children's camps, an adult fitness "
    "program, and adult art, dance, yoga, and sports programs."
  source {
    url: "https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/place-listing/jack-purcell-community-centre"
    _date {
