facilities {
  name: "Lansdowne Park"
  description:
    "Lansdowne has something for everyone. The Aberdeen Pavilion and Horticulture Building are home to a variety of "
    "events and activities. Other features include the civic garden, water plaza, children’s play area, skate park and "
    "skating court. Visitors are welcome to use the park daily from 5 am to 11 pm."
