facilities {
  name: "Lowertown Community Centre and Pool"
  description:
    "This facility is conveniently located in a downtown location with ample free parking for clients. Lowertown Pool "
    "has five-lanes typically set-up with two average lanes and two wider lanes. It also has a sauna and clean, "
    "spacious change rooms. During leisure and family swims, clients can also use the Tarzan rope and diving board."
