facilities {
  name: "Minto Recreation Complex - Barrhaven"
  description:
    "The Minto Recreation Complex - Barrhaven was recently listed by Chatelaine Magazine as one of the top 10 best "
    "indoor pools in Canada! Read the Best Indoor Pools in Canada article. The Minto Recreation Complex - Barrhaven "
    "includes a six lane, 25 metre lap pool with three metre and one metre diving boards, and an access ramp (Pool "
    "Rentals, please contact mrcb@ottawa.ca). Two NHL sized ice rinks (one rink is accessible), with accessible change "
    "rooms (please contact City Wide Allocations sports@ottawa.ca for ice rentals). Outside find an artificial turf "
    "sports field designed to meet CFL and FIFA design standards (please contact City Wide Allocations "
    "sports@ottawa.ca for field rentals). Artwork suspended from the ceiling named Mr. Kurokawa. Minto, an active "
    "sponsor of community initiatives, is proud to be associated with the City of Ottawa's Community Champions "
    "Program."
  source {
    url: "https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/place-listing/minto-recreation-complex-barrhaven"
