  description:
    "A truly unique space to pursue your talents and artistic aspirations. Rent a studio The Nepean Creative Arts "
    "Centre's arts-specific studios are available for rent, including: Specialized studios equipped for visual and "
    "performing arts. Dance studios with sprung floors, barres and floor-to-ceiling mirrors. Soundproofed music "
    "studios, Black box theatre, Recital hall, Set construction workshop, Meeting rooms. Room rental form"
