facilities {
  name: "Ottawa South Community Centre"
  description:
    "The Ottawa South Community Centre is nestled in the heart of Old Ottawa South. The centre offers a wide variety "
    "of recreation programs in partnership with the Ottawa South Community Association. Please visit the Old Ottawa "
    "South Community Association website to view their programs. A variety of rooms at Ottawa South Community Centre "
    "can be rented through the City of Ottawa. Whether it is a meeting, children’s birthday party or a small wedding "
    "we can help with your rental needs."
  source {
    url: "https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/place-listing/ottawa-south-community-centre"
    _date {
