facilities {
  name: "Overbrook Community Centre"
  description:
    "Newly renovated, this “Green” community facility is located just off the Queensway. The updated building boasts "
    "many environmental design features to create a healthier indoor environment for all our users. Our full size, "
    "sprung, hardwood floor gymnasium and dance studio allow us to offer a wide selection of specialized fitness "
    "programs. Our state of the art media rooms are home to a variety of activities and courses. Looking for a new "
    "venue for your next office event or community meeting? Check out the new Overbrook Community Centre!"
  source {
    url: "https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/place-listing/overbrook-community-centre"
    _date {
