facilities {
  name: "Sandy Hill Community Centre"
  description:
    "This busy facility offers a wide range of recreational programs in both official languages. Within this fully "
    "accessible building you will find various meeting rooms, a main hall (banquet capacity 140), boardroom, patio "
    "area, three public access computers and much more. In the adjoining award winning park you will find multiple "
    "play structures, green space, a wading pool, a ping pong table and a seasonal outdoor rink."
  source {
    url: "https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/place-listing/sandy-hill-community-centre"
