facilities {
  name: "Splash Wave Pool"
  description:
    "The name says it all! Splash is one of three wave pools located in Ottawa. Wave pools provide the perfect "
    "destination for visitors to our city including bus tours and group outings. Residents can also enjoy the \"surf\" "
    "or take a leisurely swim when the waves are off. There is also a kiddie pool with spray fountains and whirlpool. "
    "The facility also boasts a brand new 25 metre lap pool with an accessible ramp and a new 32 metre waterslide!"
  source {
    url: "https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/place-listing/splash-wave-pool"
