facilities {
  name: "Tony Graham Recreation Complex - Kanata"
  description:
    "Tony Graham Recreation Complex – Kanata offers a wide selection of recreation programs for all ages including "
    "children's summer camps, preschool programs and fitness classes. The complex includes recreation program space "
    "and two full-size arenas (Tom Flood Arena and Garry Burke Rink) with spectator seating. Ideal to rent for "
    "meetings, gatherings or social events. The Tony Graham Recreation Complex – Kanata is located in Walter Baker "
    "Park surrounded by various sports fields, park, a splash pad and toboggan hill."
  source {
    url: "https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/place-listing/tony-graham-recreation-complex-kanata"
