facilities {
  name: "Walter Baker Sports Centre"
  description:
    "Walter Baker Sports Centre in Barrhaven includes a fitness centre with treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, rowing "
    "machines, stair climber, cable machines, free weights and independent sound system and televisions. Our pool is a "
    "8-lane 25m pool; diving tank with two 1m and 3m diving boards; warm teaching pool with ramp access and preschool "
    "pool. Two full-sized ice rinks (Arena A and B) with spectator seating."
  source {
    url: "https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/place-listing/walter-baker-sports-centre"
